g-tings@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ting-tings@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ting-tings@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ting-tings">Ting Tings</a>宣布了一张名为“ Home”的新专辑的详细信息。查看下面的详细信息，以及主单曲“好人做坏事”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/indie-sleaze-revival-the-maccabees-the-horrors-white-heat-3162006"><b>“有一种乐观感”：&#39;00s独立sleaze如何使大规模复出</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>即将到来的唱片今天宣布（2月28日），将标志着他们六年来的第一张新唱片，此后从2018年发行的《黑光》和第二年推出的“曼彻斯特版本”。</p><p>由Jules de Martino＆Katie White组成的二人组于6月6日发行，从70年代阳光普照的西海岸汲取了灵感。这包括对和声和安排时代的点头，以及让人联想到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fleetwood-mac">Fleetwood Mac</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steely-dan">Steely Dan</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dire-straits">Dire Straits</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles">Eagles</a>的时刻。</p><p>曲目的第一个预告片今天以“好人做坏事”的形式出现。它看到该小组探讨了内gui，宽恕和与我们所有人都拥有的黑暗实现和平的主题。在下面查看。 </p><p><iframe title="好人做坏事" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LKBhd_vL9Zc?list=OLAK5uy_lM6y1krUCf7bOeSyY0EQ49Kig6Qjg9hTI&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>至于整个专辑，曲目列表将捕获主单曲的相同魅力和特征，这对它具有潜在的保证感。</p><p> “在专辑周期中不断地四处走动，从英国到洛杉矶再到柏林，德马蒂诺和怀特发现了伊维萨岛作为他们的家，现在已经在那里住了很多年，”一份新的描述。</p><p> “在大流行期间有了女儿之后，他们在童年时代的基础音乐触及石上寻求救助。作为一支总是自写并制作的乐队，他们走进了自己的家庭工作室，问自己一个简单的问题？在这个深刻的不确定性的新世界中，有什么感觉呢？由此产生的歌曲在新专辑“ Home”中。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://thetingtings.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订记录，并查看以下迹象列表。</p><h2> <strong>“家庭”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>“好人做坏事”</strong><br /> <strong>“做梦”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;家&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“再见歌”</strong><br /> <strong>“获胜”</strong><br /> <strong>“在我的手中”</strong><br /> <strong>“在电线上跳舞”</strong><br /> <strong>“草地歌曲”</strong><br /> <strong>``雷声&#39;&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;向下&#39;</strong> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGdxPzoN7O4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,6